Titolo: The Adventure of Little Ralph

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: The Adventure of Little Ralph is a 1999 Japanese video game for the PlayStation. It was developed by the New Corporation and released only in Japan. It is a 2D action platform game.
The game's story focuses on Ralph, a man who has been turned into a child who now must save a damsel in distress. Reviewers praised the game for its high quality graphics, music, and difficulty.